{"tid":551853,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[Kickstarter] 全球最醜惡黑警boardgame上線啦!","createTime":"2018-02-06T04:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T11:25:29.000Z","uid":43487,"like":143,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb9ff3d2e3eba04b8500edaca84dd99890a1296","tid":551853,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RgcyVun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRgcyVun.jpg&h=3e1e2c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前文:<br />\n<br />\n(極醜惡Boardgame) 震驚800萬人! 黑警貪污證據確鑿!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/481214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/481214/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ltTqhEq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FltTqhEq.png&h=0de19002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地隻boardgame終於上左kickstarter啦!<br />\n<br />\n我地之前本身有寫2月1日上kickstarter, 但時間實在太緊絀, 我地最後要delay到今日先上架, 真係唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Kickstarter link: <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/308554134/billionaire-sergeant-a-game-about-betrayal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2F308554134%2Fbillionaire-sergeant-a-game-about-betrayal&d=59m6LSno3kRCi69zNBsbmywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3a75b2fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/308554134/billionaire-sergeant-a-game-about-betrayal</a></div><br />\n<br />\n(Early Bird只有48小時, 到2月8日的中午12點!)<br />\n<br />\n介紹多次隻game先：<br />\n<br />\n『千億探長』是一個關於背叛與懷疑的遊戲。遊戲中，玩家會隨著遊戲的進度選擇(或被迫)轉變陣營，你可以堅守信念與隊友共同勝利；倒戈投靠敵人；甚至可以背叛隊友單獨勝利。你沒有永遠的敵人，也沒有永遠的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n『千億探長』與其他身份類型遊戲最大的分別，就是在遊戲中會有變節的機會。每個廉潔警員均有機會收受賄款(來自貪污警員及探長)而變節成貪污警員，勝利條件變更為貪污警員一樣；已變節的貪污警員也有可能被其他玩家暗中燒毀賄款而&quot;洗白&quot;。<br />\n同一陣營愈多人不代表該陣營會有較高的勝算，相反，你有時可能需要暗中嫁禍或背刺某些隊友才可以勝利。 記住，在千億探長內，你不能相信任何一位&quot;隊友&quot;，因為他們也可能在為自己的單獨勝利而密謀鋪路。你只能相信自己的野心!<br />\n<br />\n俾d圖大家睇下, 已經係接近final version<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3ktWnd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3ktWnd4.png&h=60f828c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eF0sDFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeF0sDFJ.jpg&h=7e7c413e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jp3YEYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjp3YEYk.jpg&h=35be46cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGame Setup:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dxYbr23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdxYbr23.jpg&h=bfd2e658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於喺kickstarter launch啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔買都可以幫手share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (share facebook page個post 仲有機會得到我地隻game)<br />\n有咩update會喺呢度, fb同ig同步更新adore<br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fheadblownstudio%2F&d=59m6LSno3kRCi69zNBsbmywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7ecaea79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio/</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/headblownstudio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fheadblownstudio%2F&d=59m6LSno3kRCi69zNBsbmywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2e33a810\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/headblownstudio/</a>"},{"pid":"b56d2b3ef400aea00f